data.description: Are you looking for a large home on One full acre that's close to I-25, Loveland, Ft Collins, or Greeley?  Look no further as this lovely ranch-style home has 3 bedrooms, 3 baths, and tons of space.  The construction on this home includes extra thick foam/cement walls and a cement tile roof. This will keep your utilities low all year. The kitchen has Tharp cabinets, a breakfast bar, a separate dining room with wood floors, and a gas fireplace. The basement includes a large great room and a pool table with more room for all your games! The yard is gorgeous with trees, flowers, and fountains. There is tons of parking and even an RV station and storage. Gorgeous Mountain Views top it off!
